                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">YES - IN SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold"></emph>
                                <emph type="bold">NO - OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0">
                            <para>Remove Speedometer/Tachometer module and make sure the odometer is plugged securely
                                into the module circuit board.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0">
                            <para>Good connection.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0">
                            <para>Connect and retest.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0">
                            <para>Disconnect odometer lead and momentarily apply 12V across the odometer leads. Each
                                time power is applied, the odometer should increment.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0">
                            <para>Odometer increments.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0">
                            <para>Replace Speedometer/ Tachometer module.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0">
                            <para>Replace odometer.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
